<TEXT>
A NEW range of go-anywhere bags are available this autumn from Kangol,
the hat people.
The company has linked up with Alpa UK to produce a selection of bags
aimed at the youth market. The styling is certainly funky, ranging from
record and courier bags, to mini backpacks and rucksacks, to purses.
Naturally Kangol's big black kangaroo logo features prominently on the
bag collection. From granny hats to cool backpacks, does label branding
know no bounds?
</TEXT>
