<TEXT>
NATALIE Gray is the first girl born in her family since her
great-great-great-great grandfather David's wife produced a daughter,
Mary, in 1807. Her father, David, a policeman, and mother, Sallyann, a
nurse, of Darlington, County Durham, already have three sons.
