<DOCID>GH950919-000152</DOCID>
<DATE>950919</DATE>
<HEADLINE>Braulio chopped</HEADLINE>
<EDITION>3</EDITION>
<PAGE>6</PAGE>
<RECORDNO>976306442</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
BRASILIA: Brazil's Health Minister said he would bar anti-Aids
television advertisements featuring a talking penis named Braulio
because people with the same name complained they were being ridiculed.
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>GH950919-000153</DOCNO>
<DOCID>GH950919-000153</DOCID>
