<HEADLINE>No bail for Graf</HEADLINE>
<EDITION>3</EDITION>
<PAGE>6</PAGE>
<RECORDNO>976306443</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
MANNHEIM: Tennis star Steffi Graf's father Peter, accused of tax
evasion over his management of her winnings, lost an appeal yesterday
for release from investigative custody. He has been in prison since
August 3 and had offered more than #6.5m in bail.
</TEXT>
