<HEADLINE>Pensioner missing</HEADLINE>
<EDITION>3</EDITION>
<PAGE>3</PAGE>
<RECORDNO>976306475</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
POLICE in Midlothian yesterday appealed for help in tracing Mr John
Laing, 79, missing from his home in Bonnyrigg since 1pm on Sunday. The
pensioner is about 5ft 6in, slim, last seen wearing a sports jacket,
bonnet, and carrying a walking stick.
</TEXT>
